    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "一. TC397 Pflash"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1.TC397 Pflash swap  每个面的大小为7M，如下图："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/APP%20Silent%20Update%20Scheme%20Base%20On%20CUBAS%20Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-32-51.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/APP Silent Update Scheme Base On CUBAS Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-32-51.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2.在芯片的数据手册中，对Dflash和Pflash的操作有明确的规定，即Dflash和Pflash不能同时进行操作，一次只能操作一个，所以需要使用MemACC模块进行指令的并发处理。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "如下："
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/APP%20Silent%20Update%20Scheme%20Base%20On%20CUBAS%20Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-34-3.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/APP Silent Update Scheme Base On CUBAS Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-34-3.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "二. FOTA 功能"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. 功能框图"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/APP%20Silent%20Update%20Scheme%20Base%20On%20CUBAS%20Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-35-15.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/APP Silent Update Scheme Base On CUBAS Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-35-15.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "1.1 在app模式下，增加DiagGw、DiagR、DiagProxy模块来处理接收的升级数据；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "1.2 在app模式下的配置工程中增加DiagProxy PduR和Dcm的连接配置；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "1.3 在app模式下，增加升级相关的诊断服务，如10 60，31 01 ff 00，34，36，37，31 01 02 02，31 01 02 05；以及调用MemAcc接口的Flash hanle服务函数；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "1.4 Infineon TC397 不能同时操作DFlash和PFlash，集成这个模块，实现DFlash和PFlash的互斥访问；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 4,
      "text": "1.5 在app模式下，增加SysStateHandle服务，用来处理接收到的swap bank指令以及读取scc information的指令；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "2. 升级流程图"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/APP%20Silent%20Update%20Scheme%20Base%20On%20CUBAS%20Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-37-50.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/APP Silent Update Scheme Base On CUBAS Stack/image-2026-2-26_17-37-50.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "三. 切面功能"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3.1 在app模式下接收到切面指令后，会存储一个标志到Retention Ram中；这个标志是BL和app共享的标志；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3.2 在升级完后接收到下电指令，app会判断下电指令的类型，如果是升级完且下电的指令，app则会reset，并设置重启目标为BL；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3.3 在进入BL后，会在上电之前运行swap函数，然后进行reset；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3.4 经过上面的过程后，mcu就完成了切面并重启的过程；"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "四. app 下实现升级的模块路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4.1 bosch应用逻辑控制路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": ".\\Config\\Autosar\\Application\\SilentUpdate\\"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4.2 cubas 代码逻辑路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": ".\\Config\\Autosar\\stdcore\\Cubas\\CubasBSWCfgTemp\\SilenceUpdate_CubasFbl\\"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4.3 地址配置文件路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": ".\\Config\\Autosar\\stdcore\\Cubas\\CubasBSWCfgTemp\\SilenceUpdate_CubasFbl\\Cubas_FblCfg\\ApplicationLayer\\rba_BldrCmp\\api\\ rba_BldrCmp_Cfg_LogBlkHdl.h"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4.4 实际切面文件路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": ". \\Bootloader\\Config\\Bootloader\\SilentUpdate_SwapBank\\"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "五. 初始化函数的调用路径"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5.1"
